headline: Apple's Tim Cook reportedly on Capitol Hill, Oracle earnings watch

Meanwhile, Apple (AAPL) CEO Tim Cook is reportedly on Capitol Hill in Washington, D.C., talking to lawmakers about tech safeguards to protect children, according to reporting from Punchbowl. headline: Oracle Stock: Prepare For Q2 Earnings With A Short-Term, High-Risk Spread Trade
